---
title: Italian Lamb & Baby Spinach Pie with Potato & Parmesan Topping
description: Sometimes only a pie will do. Satisfy that craving for something warm, herby and comforting with this rich, cheesy mash-topped number. It's Nanna's cooking fused with an explosion of flavour and a dinner that reminds us why at-home cooking is best.
